{"tid":38851,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我阿媽唔鐘意我女朋友，可以點算","createTime":"2016-12-14T07:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:44:02.000Z","uid":65120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"598c377acde2a8eaa239fb8647c85646cd16a145","tid":38851,"uid":65120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"又話佢年紀大過我唔夠靚，又嫌佢住唐樓，又話佢有癲癇以後生既小朋友可能身體會有問題<br />\n<br />\n但我好想繼續同佢一齊，我可以點做說服我阿媽?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc33bea7db469a2e543248688265576ec2e25b6","tid":38851,"uid":65120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5dca8e28b81982788c576a851f002371f8c384fd","tid":38851,"uid":15221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"換個阿媽"},{"pid":"b7493768dc345da527c68a95529c8128020bd28d","tid":38851,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d01bcd3ca68e10c136b1d7d4ce671fdbee8f1fda","tid":38851,"uid":28892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:48:23.000Z","msg":"佢係你嘅女朋友定係你媽嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e2954babe2713daf8f0f9cefaa78581f55f298","tid":38851,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"比佢中出"},{"pid":"e55eba9818ad495e063759baffad79de87d75394","tid":38851,"uid":25950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"屌鳩你老母啦<br />\n如果你條垃圾揀條女都要俾阿媽左右<br />\n你放過條女唔好累人累物啦"},{"pid":"4f851a142057a94b8ccb062f254ed95335690fb3","tid":38851,"uid":21461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"你話識左某一個，然後帶個男既返去食飯<br />\n佢就唔會唔鐘意你女朋友架啦"},{"pid":"ccc4a665d943fc3f025bafec628b73b361cb0550","tid":38851,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:52